      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Andrei Fortuna</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:128px;\"><a href=\"/File:AndreiFortuna.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/0/0c/AndreiFortuna.jpg\" width=\"126\" height=\"170\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:AndreiFortuna.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Andrei Fortuna <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Andrei Fortuna</b>,<br />\na Romanian software developer and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freelancer\">freelancer</a>, who has worked on a widerange of projects, such as chess engine programming, 3d engines, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_search_engine\">Web search engine</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Email_client\">e-mail software</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Online_auction\">online auction</a> sites \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nAndrei is author the <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> programs <i>Chess176</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and the <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/Freyr\" title=\"Freyr\">Freyr</a>. \nIn 2001, Andrei developed the <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a> Web search engine of the pre 2006 forum software <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrei_Fortuna&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=30905&amp;p=117120\">New Winboard Program</a> by <a href=\"/%C4%90or%C4%91e_Vidanovi%C4%87\" title=\"Đorđe Vidanović\">Đorđe Vidanović</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 15, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=98762\">A New Release of my Amateur Chess Engine Freyr</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrei Fortuna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 22, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=102792\">A Question on simple Alpha-Beta versus PVS/Negascout</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrei Fortuna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 21, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a>, <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a>, <a href=\"/NegaScout\" title=\"NegaScout\">NegaScout</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=197527\">CCC Search Engine is available&#160;!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrei Fortuna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 15, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=337347\">Crafty (under winboard) question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Andrei Fortuna</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Algebraic_Chess_Notation#SAN\" title=\"Algebraic Chess Notation\">Standard Algebraic Notation (SAN)</a>, <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrei_Fortuna&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20020224143312/http://planet-source-code.com/vb/authors/ShowAuthorBio.asp?lngAuthorId=285062&amp;lngWId=3\">About Andrei Fortuna</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Andrei_Fortuna&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.planet-source-code.com/vb/scripts/ShowCode.asp?txtCodeId=3333&amp;lngWId=3\">Planet Source Code™ | Freyr - A Chess Playing Program</a>, image archived</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20020224143312/http://planet-source-code.com/vb/authors/ShowAuthorBio.asp?lngAuthorId=285062&amp;lngWId=3\">About Andrei Fortuna</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=411300&amp;t=39467\">Re: The very first Romanian chess engine - Chess 176/1</a> by <a href=\"/Jim_Ablett\" title=\"Jim Ablett\">Jim Ablett</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 24, 2011</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=197749\">Thanks a million to Andrei Fortuna!!!</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Schwartz\" title=\"Steven Schwartz\">Steven Schwartz</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 15, 2001</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301042712\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.020 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 71/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 162/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTr